    <title/Loop Support/
    <author.Extern to="author.db" key="Denys.Duchier">
    <Abstract>
Starting in Mozart 1.1.0, there is now convenient syntactic support
for loops.  This document is divided in two chapters: the first one
describes what is officially supported in Mozart 1.1.1, the second one
documents the experimental extensions which are not supported, and are
subject to change or removal without notice.  However, we would
appreciate feedback from the user community to help us shape the
future of these extensions should they be found useful.
    </Abstract>
